FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780185774
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient spared chemo
OL,4,Cthrough trial says it felt 'like
OL,5,CChristmas'
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FInstead of chemotherapy, she received
OL,13,Fradiotherapy and hormone therapy, and
OL,14,Fcompleted eight years of active
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FAlmost nine years on from her
OL,18,Fdiagnosis, Ms Bonham said she does not
OL,19,Ffeel defined by cancer, has returned
OL,20,Fto normal family life, and enjoys
OL,21,Fkeeping active, walking and yoga.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
