PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780185774
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient spared chemo
OL,4,Cthrough trial says it felt 'like
OL,5,CChristmas'
OL,7,FThe trial's chief investigator, and
OL,8,Fprofessor of breast oncology at the
OL,9,FUCL Cancer Institute, Professor Rob
OL,10,FStein, said: "These results mark an
OL,11,Fimportant and significant step toward
OL,12,Fmore personalised treatment.
OL,14,F"The trial has successfully used
OL,15,Ftumour biology to guide decisions
OL,16,Frather than relying solely on
OL,17,Ftraditional clinical features.
OL,26,@rD@NOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
