OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780185774
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient spared chemo
OL,4,Cthrough trial says it felt 'like
OL,5,CChristmas'
OL,7,F"For patients, this means many may be
OL,8,Fspared the physical and emotional
OL,9,Fburden of chemotherapy and its
OL,10,Fpotential long-term side effects.
OL,12,F"For health systems, it represents a
OL,13,Fmore efficient and evidence-based use
OL,14,Fof resources."
OL,16,FIt is not known whether the findings
OL,17,Fapply to people under the age of 40,
OL,18,FUCL said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
