OL,3,CBreast cancer patient spared chemo
OL,4,Cthrough trial says it felt 'like
OL,5,CChristmas'
OL,7,FIt is hoped that more information
OL,8,Fabout the use of the gene test for pre-
OL,9,Fmenopausal women will emerge in the
OL,10,Fnext phase of the trial, but a result
OL,11,Fis "still several years away", the
OL,12,Funiversity added.
